            "text": "<p>The <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-emerald\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"emerald cut\">emerald cut</a> is for the woman who values composure and class. Its long, open facets and mirror-like effects bring a sense of calm elegance, nothing flashy, just refined confidence. It’s favorite among brides with modern yet minimalist aesthetics.<br/>Say yes if you admire subtlety and structure.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
