          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/6_fa23b6a8-0c9e-44e9-b389-07d401e75011.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A teardrop shaped diamond encircled by a halo of smaller stones. This ring elongates the finger and sparkles from every angle, blending vintage charm with modern brilliance.</p><p>Say yes if you love designs that are soft yet striking. This modern engagement ring bridges classic romance with contemporary charm.</p>",
