            "text": "<p>Three <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-pear\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pear shaped\">pear shaped</a> diamonds come together to create a design that's soft and dynamic. It is modern yet sentimental, and its fluid shape adds movement to sparkle. It is a beautiful option for someone who believes love keeps growing through every stage and season. </p>",
